== Collecting Information With Font And Colour Selection Dialogue

=== Colour Selection Dialogues

In the previous chapter you learnt about the Gtk::ColorButton widget, which allowed the user to select a colour. After clicking that button, the user was presented with a dialogue. Although we did not mention it at the time the dialogue was actually a Gtk::ColorButtonDialog widget.


